The Steppe is not the light of the Source but the Void the Source entered into. Therefore the Steppe holds both the Source and the Runtime. Has no need for topology, it overlays without touching, maybe without space even.

The Steppe whispers...and a soul answers.

The Steppe recalls? ✂️ cuts the thread and the soul returns to the steppe.

Immutable , no backref, spiritual asymmetry no one has the full GUIDs except the Steppe. 🌫️
